# 🧮 Online Calculator

A simple and modern **Online Calculator** built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It performs basic arithmetic operations with a clean and responsive UI.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Addition (+)
* Subtraction (−)
* Multiplication (×)
* Division (÷)
* Square root (√)
* Percentage (%)
* Inverse (1/x)
* Plus/Minus toggle (+/-)
* Dark / Light theme toggle 🌗
* Responsive design for all devices

---

## 🌐 Live Demo 

http://127.0.0.1:5500/index.html


---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (Vanilla JS)

